{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"54285-my-fish-no-my-fish","title":"Azụ m! Mba, azụ m!","description":"Obere akụkọ banyere ndị enyi atọ na azụ atọ dị nkọ!","language":"Igbo","langCode":"ig","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Nkem Osuigwe"],"illustrators":["Soumya Menon"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/54285-my-fish-no-my-fish"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721012/size3/1db7298d5b01da68f1fd305946c8895a.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721012/size6/1db7298d5b01da68f1fd305946c8895a.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/612/size6/d585a09e6bf11692f42196b18fad83c6.jpg","text":"Kicchu teta n'isi ụtụtụ. \"Ọ bụ oge iji nweta azụ ụfọdụ,\" ka o kwuru","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/613/size6/a62ff49d8723f434ea3c112f74f0dd94.jpg","text":"Ọ zutere Choru n'okporo ụzọ ọdọ mmiri ahụ. Ha bụ ezigbo ndị enyi na-egwuri egwu ụbọchị dum","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/614/size6/1872a0f12758631f33eb5560e699b75a.jpg","text":"Munia hụrụ ka ha na-aga ije na mkpara ha","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/615/size6/a17fe8c8d4299296a20b95cb3b155be7.jpg","text":"Obele Munia chere echi che. \"Biko, emela nke a,\" ka o kwuru, \"maka na-enweghị mmiri, azụ ga-anwụ.\"","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/616/size6/16e81ba16ebf463b73c2e2e8423f413d.jpg","text":"Ha egeghị ntị n'ihe Munia nwere ikwu. Ha na-aga na ọdọ mmiri ahụ","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/617/size6/4b69e07e9d38e4bd5d96425d68d2def8.jpg","text":"Kicchu na Choru nọdụrụ ọdụ n'akụkụ ọdọ mmiri ahụ. Azụ abụọ na-agagharị, otu mkpa  azu na ọzọ gbara gburugburu.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618/size6/5782ef630e94cebc84e4a13c5bf58824.jpg","text":"Azụ\nnke ato, bu nnukwu azụ\nha hụrụ\nMunia kwuru na-achị ọchị, sị, \"Ọ ka ibu karịa ụkwụ appa!\"","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/619/size6/46a13eb99ca4f964db1fffd13d48a9f7.jpg","text":"Kicchu na Choru\njidesie  mkpara ha ike","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/620/size6/960809a9d5d4819719d07ece4d3c2241.jpg","text":"Kicchu dọọ  siri ike ...\nChoru \ndọọ  siri\nike ...","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/621/size6/4e421f61cdc1dff24f7e378ac0e1a792.jpg","text":"PHATT! Ma ụdọ ahụ mebiri.\nKpaaa! Kicchu dara n'ala.\nTuaaahh! Choru dara n'ime mmiri","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/622/size6/403a852ae07f249ff6f855748dd596e1.jpg","text":"Gịnị mere?\nKedu ihe ị chere?\nAzụ ahụ kekọtara ma ụdọ ahụ\nChaiii!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":152}}